  "abstract": "This study underscores the potential of integrating advanced language models with clinical coding processes to improve documentation accuracy. ChatGPT 4 demonstrated improved consistency and comparable performance to median human coders, achieving 22% accuracy in challenging cases. Combining ChatGPT with methods like SNOMED mapping could further enhance clinical coding accuracy, particularly for complex scenarios.",
